{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"A\n    \n      Asteroid Belt\n      Dense debris field between Mars and Jupiter. Rocks of varying size — small ones chip hull on contact, large ones are navigational obstacles. Could contain salvageable resources or hidden enemy bases.","choice":"asteroids","id":null,"timestamp":1775267907365}
